data.description:
Walking distance to downtown and the new sports stadium! Beautiful refinished wood floors throughout. New master bedroom on main floor with master bath, walk in closet and office space!. Upstairs bath remodeled and upgraded! Main floor laundry area, w/d hookups. Alley access. 2 bedrooms upper, 1 main bedroom suit. 
NO pets, NO smoking in/out

one year possibly 2, NO PETS and NO SMOKING. Tenant pays all utilities
